FBIS4-54568 "dreeu085_d_94007" FBIS-EEU-94-085 Daily Report 2 May 1994 SLOVAKIA President Kovac Appoints Sitko as Media Adviser President Kovac Appoints Sitko as Media Adviser LD0205194094 Bratislava STV 1 Television Network in Slovak 1730 GMT 2 May 94 LD0205194094 Bratislava STV 1 Television Network Slovak BFN [Text] Slovak President Michal Kovac recalled Josef Sitko from the post of director of the Press Department of the Office of the President of the Slovak Republic and appointed him as media adviser, effective 1 May.
